" Activate/Deactivate the file exploration window
map <F9> <Esc>:NERDTreeToggle<CR>

" Display/mask the TagList window
map <F8> <Esc>:TlistToggle<CR>

" Activate Django autocompletion
map <F10><Esc>:call SetAutoDjangoCompletion()<CR>

" Open a class definition/function with Rope
map <F6><Esc>:RopeGoToDefinition<CR>

" Rename a class or a variable with Rope
map <F7><Esc>:RopeRename<CR>

